description:
C&B talk to Fox & Friends co-host Brian Kilmeade, author of The President and the Freedom Fighter: Abraham Lincoln, Frederick Douglass, and Their Battle to Save America's Soul. CNN Doctor: Mask with your vaxed relatives at Christmas. Buck's 40th birthday. CNN celebrates 5-cent drop in gas prices. 5-star podcast reviews. C&B take calls.
